247da6820879623ad3ae1f02b7e8907801056a3","tid":2492154,"uid":97979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:00:38.000Z","msg":"TOW用嚟打戰車坦克<br />\n上唔上到1千架坦克咁多？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"可能攻金門當攻台勝利呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"我怕攻金門都係打到成pat屎咁，反而嚇到唔敢攻台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"唔洗打啦，台灣人送比佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57ac9bf7eb004a5536d35ff1b6c28f06dc43617","tid":2492154,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc072ab7aff05ecd473211b1f7dc7deadbeb721a","tid":2492154,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法國都黎做架兩<br />\n<br />\n〔記者鍾麗華／台北報導〕我國海軍6艘原名拉法葉級的康定級巡防艦的火力升級案，預計向法國軍火商軍購升級套件，雙方也已敲定合約，繼中國外交部日前表達不滿後，中國國防部今天（15日）發出新聞稿稱，中方堅決反對任何國家向台灣出售武器，堅決反對任何國家與台灣開展軍事聯繫，要求法方立即撤銷有關對台軍售專案。<br />\n<br />\n法國外交部長勒德里安13日表示，在1994年法中宣言框架內，法國承認「一個中國」政策，並繼續呼籲兩岸進行對話，「法國也嚴格遵循與台灣締結的契約性質承諾，自從1994年以來，從未改變」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國國防部發言人任國強今天稱，「世界上只有一個中國，台灣是中國不可分割的一部分。中方堅決反對任何國家向台灣出售武器，堅決反對任何國家與台灣開展軍事聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n任國強說，「中方要求法方立即撤銷有關對台軍售專案，以免對兩國兩軍關係造成進一步損害。中國軍隊有堅定的意志、充分的信心和足夠的能力，挫敗任何形式的外部勢力干涉和『台獨』分裂行徑，堅定捍衛國家主權和領土完整，堅定維護台海地區和平穩定。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3166934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3166934&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=697d84b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3166934&h=1fbf120a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3166934</a>"},{"pid":"e948a500025467c095941061eb2a139f6b570caf","tid":2492154,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"俾咩裝備台狗都冇用<br />\n根本冇錢main<br />\n同埋到時要用都未必有人識用<br />\n佢哋軍訓連手榴彈都係用汽水罐代替<br />\n邊有可能俾真嘢你操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要軍演就check下邊支用得就拎幾支出嚟<br />\n其他都係鋪塵"},{"pid":"96addef5b5cb0d7665988f9b8ae2c005f49b5fc5","tid":2492154,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV8FvV335S1C7rovLPoFjP8GWdmEaxST8tjRZBBEXr5VF?filename=cWWwCNo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWWwCNo.gif&h=4dc58c99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bab0e70cd839f43825727c529fa2c0cfcc05d7a","tid":2492154,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01834904852a29bc32655c7342263384a29b2d6","tid":2492154,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c506dc726ec6026c714443ece252bff70f2bb2b","tid":2492154,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e948a500025467c095941061eb2a139f6b570caf","tid":2492154,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"俾咩裝備台狗都冇用<br />\n根本冇錢main<br />\n同埋到時要用都未必有人識用<br />\n佢哋軍訓連手榴彈都係用汽水罐代替<br />\n邊有可能俾真嘢你操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要軍演就check下邊支用得就拎幾支出嚟<br />\n其他都係鋪塵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"咩都無用係咪訓響度等人黎接收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e862ef58c374a19b5d1bd6087475d1004f